=== Before ===
def @main(%x: Tensor[(4), float32]) {
  multiply(%x, 2f)
}

=== After ===
def @main(%x: Tensor[(4), float32] /* ty=Tensor[(4), float32] */) -> Tensor[(4), float32] {
  add(%x, %x) /* ty=Tensor[(4), float32] */
}


Pass执行逻辑：
MyOptimizePass
    -> transform_function(func)
        -> Mul2ToAdd().visit(func)
            -> 遍历函数体
            -> 遇到 Call
            -> visit_call
            -> multiply(x, 2.0) 改成 add(x, x)

整体执行逻辑：
import tvm / relay
    ↓
定义 ExprMutator: Mul2ToAdd
    ↓
定义 FunctionPass: MyOptimizePass
    ↓
构造 Relay IR: x * 2.0
    ↓
打印 Before
    ↓
执行 Sequential:
    1. InferType
    2. MyOptimizePass
        - 遍历 Relay Function
        - 找到 multiply(x, 2.0)
        - 替换成 add(x, x)
    3. InferType
    ↓
打印 After
